snippet.title: Lone Wolf : A Werewolf Post Apocalyptic Beat-Em Up RPG
snippet.description: Lone Wolf: A Post Apocalyptic Beat-Em Up Role Playing Game. This action/adventure game lets a player use martial arts skills, weapons, and turn into a werewolf to fight their way through a world set in the aftermath of post nuclear devastation.
